<p>Reports incorrect observer method definitions.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Must contain only one <code>@Observes</code> parameter</li>
  <li>Cannot have parameters annotated with <code>@Disposes</code></li>
  <li>Cannot be annotated with <code>@Inject</code> and <code>@Produces</code></li>
</ul>
